    ‚àá files‚Üêopts FindFile file;files
    ‚çù find a single file, allowing dotted extensions
      :If ‚éïNEXISTS file ‚ãÑ files‚Üê,‚äÇ,file ‚ãÑ :Return ‚ãÑ :EndIf  ‚çù file exists : fine
