    ‚àá {r}‚Üêto Relocate from;i;nextfrom;nextto;tmpfile
    ‚çù move list of files, updating file names as we go through the list
      r‚Üê‚ç¨
      :While ~0‚àä‚ç¥to
          (nextto nextfrom)‚Üê‚äÉ¬®(to from) ‚ãÑ (to from)‚Üì‚ç®‚Üê1
          :If nextto‚â¢nextfrom
              :Trap 22
                  r,‚Üênextto ‚éïNMOVE nextfrom
              :Else ‚çù Suspect issue with case sensitive file system
                  :If (‚éïC nextto)‚â°‚éïC nextfrom ‚çù Names differ only in case
                      tmpfile‚Üê(739‚å∂0),'/Utils.Relocate_',(' '~‚ç®‚çï‚éïTS),'.linktmp'
                      tmpfile ‚éïNMOVE nextfrom  ‚çù Must move file out of current folder
                      r,‚Üênextto ‚éïNMOVE tmpfile ‚çù And then recreate with new casing
                  :Else
                      ‚éïDMX.Message ‚éïSIGNAL ‚éïEN
                  :EndIf
              :EndTrap
              from‚Üê(nextfrom ‚éïR nextto)from  ‚çù update directories in particular
          :Else ‚ãÑ r,‚Üê1   ‚çù no need to copy
          :EndIf
      :EndWhile
    ‚àá

    :EndSection





    :Section Namespaces

    ‚çù Supported name classes
